{"tid":1435424,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想學 速成同倉頡 有無咩好教材?","createTime":"2019-08-09T04:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:16:22.000Z","uid":143869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f20fe93f166334918258c6960489de913ad33043","tid":1435424,"uid":143869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"小弟學左輸入法成17年有多<br />\n都係<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">速成</span></strong>識打6成左右o既中文字<br />\n我想問下有無D好好o既教材係可以買/下載?<br />\n<br />\n我平時打字係用<br />\n方法1.打英文係查yahoo字典再copy (緊nervous)<br />\n方法2.唔識打個(識)字 就打認字 唔識打個(學)字 就打個中字 搵番個字<br />\n方法3.手寫輸入法<br />\n<br />\n小弟失緊業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想搵份office工<br />\n有無巴打可以幫幫我 推薦一下D教材俾我<br />\nMany thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我之前係用呢個網學中文輸入法<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cjhk.org/note_gm.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cjhk.org%2Fnote_gm.htm&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=c0e8e1ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cjhk.org/note_gm.htm</a>"},{"pid":"254e4ebe72fe419fa758c297185188b2dfa264b8","tid":1435424,"uid":262035,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"逼自己 wtsapp 打中文用倉頡<br />\n包你一兩個月就識"},{"pid":"305c6c64ac18ebae531538ff03f136912581908e","tid":1435424,"uid":143869,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"254e4ebe72fe419fa758c297185188b2dfa264b8","tid":1435424,"uid":262035,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"逼自己 wtsapp 打中文用倉頡<br />\n包你一兩個月就識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:59:50.000Z","msg":"真毒whatsapp冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df3644d91497e269c76cb33135a43768c5deed2","tid":1435424,"uid":262035,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"305c6c64ac18ebae531538ff03f136912581908e","tid":1435424,"uid":143869,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"254e4ebe72fe419fa758c297185188b2dfa264b8","tid":1435424,"uid":262035,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"逼自己 wtsapp 打中文用倉頡<br />\n包你一兩個月就識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:59:50.000Z","msg":"真毒whatsapp冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"咁每日倉頡連登開post 等巴絲同你傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc38f65f24acd03025532e7266f63d2e730d64c","tid":1435424,"uid":143869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:54:02.000Z","msg":"推推推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b032578e7df37a99ce35d3da22dee32608fe05ad","tid":1435424,"uid":302752,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"想當年翻學嗰陣見到miss用倉頡打字好快好型 於是用開速成嘅我就好想學<br />\n我學嗰陣就冇咩野教材嘅，每日隨意搵一篇文逐個字打，基本上我都只係base on嗰個基本取碼原則去打每一隻字，撞到唔識嘅字唔好即刻查點打，要迫自己諗點打。<br />\n久而久之，你打嘅速度就會越黎越快，唔洗諗點取碼就打到一隻字，好似我依個回覆咁樣，全程可以話係「冇用過腦」，隻手自動打我想打嘅字出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油ching，熟能生巧，堅持二字就係最好嘅教材<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf4de17942b4d12d2fea30a64c79a70e1b7411f","tid":1435424,"uid":174432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"我用電話打好快 不過用電腦就食撚哂屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db19fae6fe2abe623509d9e27493bf1d49104a84","tid":1435424,"uid":237068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"先速成後倉頡<br />\n背熟啲碼先"},{"pid":"94e0ac9fe5f679dac39e4ac3aeb095985eac9727","tid":1435424,"uid":210165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06abe08fa2dd2345aa314dd8952509bf11d76ad4","tid":1435424,"uid":18265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:25:14.000Z","msg":"用少少時間理解下倉頡嘅原理，跟住背下啲碼<br />\n背完應該都打到七成字，淨低邊用邊學"},{"pid":"8c91fe68315c3800554a4422e57c30c15062ae90","tid":1435424,"uid":268756,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"真係熟能生巧 迫自己所有輸入法都轉做倉頡<br />\n用得多就識"},{"pid":"6105d864ac7d3ce9561ce43a0135e9db7e1bb14b","tid":1435424,"uid":128164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:28:45.000Z","msg":"去書局買本倉頡教學嘅書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17cf76d26a0c78e74fb123a8110007d91500406","tid":1435424,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:32:45.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9poBP0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9poBP0w.jpg&h=0f98feec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7U0Xzsb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7U0Xzsb.jpg&h=e3df992c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zw3uqyR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZw3uqyR.jpg&h=d94faad4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHj9qyS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHj9qyS.jpg&h=e63a86a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5EY6sNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5EY6sNc.jpg&h=ee2e1c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXbvUsd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXbvUsd.png&h=b7503827&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Dz9qyT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Dz9qyT.jpg&h=f6805492&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6629808822136f3ce7cf93aafe700f7d20790ba","tid":1435424,"uid":303359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T